&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# Polyak averaging tracks an (exponential moving) average of the past parameters of a model, for use at test/evaluation time.&lt;/span&gt;
